      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i dont want someone else to carry it. i dont want to talk to a stranger or some professional. i just feel like there's no point. like i wasted all those years fighting for nothing and now i'm just empty. it feels like the only way to actually find peace is just to... stop. everything.",
